{"tid":749051,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得同居好處多定壞處多","createTime":"2018-07-19T16:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T04:49:58.000Z","uid":23479,"like":9,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"84aa0241ef0562aea396c06faebdfe508a6f958d","tid":749051,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T16:34:35.000Z","msg":"我就覺得好處多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返到屋企有人陪，可以傾下計，一齊笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但仙女覺得壞處多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話成日見易生磨擦<br />\n<br />\n一齊住冇私隱<br />\n<br />\n一齊食宵夜會易肥<br />\n<br />\n日扑夜扑會厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970f0461d77f92f341cddc815fa14ceb17f80263","tid":749051,"uid":148192,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"住得仙居多多壞處也不怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27931c985c4d290c3c04283f28ce8b522388651e","tid":749051,"uid":65847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"人夾人㗎啫"},{"pid":"cb24e6c6bc5f5c3fda8955a34affb793167f9ad7","tid":749051,"uid":23479,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"970f0461d77f92f341cddc815fa14ceb17f80263","tid":749051,"uid":148192,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"住得仙居多多壞處也不怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"都係，人潔地靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d708e0a2dff081d005a3c0f3e620dd9a4654e9","tid":749051,"uid":179547,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"好處多<br />\n<br />\n如果一齊住就不斷磨擦影響關係，咁結咗婚咪仲